Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:31.44,Shiver,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur0.6\pos(280,20)}All the holes we had to breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:34.46,Shiver,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur0.6\pos(805,20)}To make the other one leave
