Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem strange and alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Primitive and peculiar,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.97,0:01:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,they are unlike any flora or fauna known to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Since time immemorial,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.77,0:01:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,men have feared these misshapen entities,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.25,0:01:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,which came to be known as "mushi."
