Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Toki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When snow falls into the lake, what happens to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It melts and becomes part of the lake water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, why doesn't it just fall on the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow doesn't have a choice where it falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... poor snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, once the lake freezes, \Nthe snow can pile up on top of its ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When will that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as it gets a bit colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hope the lake freezes soon!
