Dialogue: 2,0:03:01.99,0:03:07.91,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\an4\fad(2000,0)\blur0.6\pos(114,109)}Beneath the Snow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be... an inn somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's buried in snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Maybe it's this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I needed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm chilled to the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We never have guests at this time of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:04:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose the only people \Nwho'd venture through this much snow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,are the really curious ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Well then, what has you so curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the snow itself. It's very interesting around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to come see it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's true we get a lot of snow in these parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just typical for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's all that interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir? Your bath is—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going to sleep soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's close this, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, these are drawings of snowflakes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I take a look through?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, there are so many different shapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a snowflake too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, that one's a type of snow mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sometimes find them if you sift through snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are things like this inside snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're especially diverse in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already found quite a few just around this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Yukinarashi, or a "Snow Smoother" mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It lives in the tracks made by animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are enough of these around, \Ntracks made in the snow disappear quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,which can be a nuisance when you're hunting or need to find someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... how about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A Yukidangomushi, or "Snow Roly-poly" mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw some on my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They move by rolling on top of the snow, making snowballs in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When their snowballs start to get too big,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,they usually crash them against trees to shake off the extra snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you stumble across one with no trees nearby, \Nit may try to crash into you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They sound pretty mischievous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When they crash into trees, the shockwaves they make sometimes cause avalanches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not as harmless as you might think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What others are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This one here is probably the rarest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This mushi likes to travel in packs \Nand stick close to a specific animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They sting the animal and steal its warmth little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When animals are "possessed" by this type of mushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,snow seems to follow them wherever they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why they're called Tokoyukimushi, or "Never-ending Snow" mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What else happens when they possess you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body temperature decreases as well. They say there's no risk of death, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They usually depart when spring comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there someone in particular you're worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,On your way here, you saw \Nthat house buried in snow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend lives there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:07:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of him that the house became buried in snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Early this winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,he lost his little sister to the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too long after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed that snow was always falling around him, and only him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Tae.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I know you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten even paler.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A mushi-shi named Ginko{-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He was wondering if he could speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for how cold it is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever we try to warm up the place, \Nmy skin starts to hurt... like it's burning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas I don't feel the cold one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How long has it been this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably ever since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a night with snow but no wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought for a second that my little sister had come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so I opened the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachi—{?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When I did, it felt as though snow had flown right into my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, come back inside, or you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, I can't stand being near anything warm,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,even though the cold doesn't bother me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,From that night on, snow's been falling wherever I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really don't feel cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I do feel bad for Mom and Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's really nothing wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I take a look at your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His hand is as cold as ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He can't even tolerate human body temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skin's turned white. You're getting frostbite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Although {\i1}you{\i0} may not feel it, your body does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't get yourself warm soon, \Nyou could lose your hands or your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But it really feels like I'm burning when I do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your senses are just being deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not actually burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. I'm fine with the way things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go catch some fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't figure out how to make him want to get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It stopped snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:10:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, something {\i1}is{\i0} wrong with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to do what's best for your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't follow me. It's not safe out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been really out of it lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The snow falling into the lake isn't melting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never knew it could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:12:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's the case, maybe snow can pile up \Nat the bottom of the lake too... huh, Sachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The lake's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't—{stand there!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The snow is... only in one spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Did you check over there{ too}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He must be under there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That part of the lake is just too deep. \NWe {just }can't dive there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun's down, too. It's too cold for us to go into the water now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That night, blistering cold descended upon the entire village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a single night, the lake became completely frozen over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not snowing anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a bad feeling that this might happen someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've stopped you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I should never have let you \Ngo out on the lake by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The lake's ice must be contracting and cracking from the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Your mind is playing tricks on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tae{-chan}, Toki's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But he wandered off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He had really bad frostbite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So we tried to warm him up, \Nbut then he ran away like he was burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's split up and find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't treat him soon, it might be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll check the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It really {\i1}is{\i0} you, Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to get you some help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Sachi's just asleep \Nat the bottom of the lake like I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Beneath the snow, at the bottom of the lake, I was asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard the ice cracking, I woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she just hasn't woken up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can help her—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachi's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, you jumped in after her and dragged her out of the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You held her as she grew colder and colder... \Nuntil she died in your arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not know what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tae... Don't stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Get on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My back is burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tae's heart is still burning hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My cheek stings...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see my breath, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My hands and feet hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so cold that I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tae?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps because the scant warmth remaining in Tae's body had warmed him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toki regained normal use of his senses by the time he returned to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the constant snow around him \Nhad somehow stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Both suffered from frostbite, \Nbut Tae's frostbite was fortunately minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toki's was severe. He lost several fingers and toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it was miraculous enough that he returned alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that snow protecting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When I woke up, I was covered in it, \Nas though it were a blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it all a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're really leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If I put it off any longer, \NI won't be able to leave till spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You too. Take good care of yourselves until spring comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, winter's only just begun here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a land blanketed by white snow throughout most of the year,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it is not the water or the earth,{Comma for "but" emphasis.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but the snow that conceals \Nmany of these misshapen entities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come inside and warm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Atop the snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}within the snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and beneath the snow.
